      "title": "Prime Minister's house on fire; Three arrested",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "3 people have been arrested by the Kollupitiya police in connection with the burning of Prime Minister Ranil Wickremesinghe's private house last night.",
        "The police said that one of the three arrested is a 19-year-old from Kalgissa area and the others are from Gadawatta and Galli areas."
      ],
